Class ReversiModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • ReversiModel

  • public class ReversiModel
extends java.util.Observable
    ReversiModel holds game data for Reversi. Game data includes the state of the board, the scores, the current player, and legal moves.
    Author:
    DennyHo and Ryan Luu
